    <id>Midori</id>
    <version>0.1.0.0</version>
    <title>Midori - Sweetens the Psake build experience with common helpers for
        SQL, HipChat, WinRM, PsGet, Jenkins</title>
    <authors>Ethan Brown</authors>
    <owners>Ethan Brown</owners>
    <summary>Psake build tool helpers, with basic support for Jenkins build
        server, SQL database creation and script-running, HipChat notifications,
        PsGet integration PsGet, WinRM helpers and a number of misc PS tasks.</summary>
    <description>Midori includes a number of helpers for common functionality
        needed during builds, including:
        * Sql - Create dbs with SMO, execute SQL scripts. Ship MDBs as part of
        a build, or run intgration tests against a fresh DB.
        * HipChat - send notifications
        * PsGet - Install PsGet and gain access to libraries such as PsCx
        * WinRM - Run code on remote servers, by exporting local PSM1 modules
        to remote machines
        * Jenkins - Download assets stored in S3
        * Misc helpers - Safer transcription, better error logging, and other
        common usage helpers
    </description>
    <requireLicenseAcceptance>false</requireLicenseAcceptance>
    <releaseNotes>
        * First release - includes Jenkins build asset downloading, SQL SMO db
        creation, HipChat notifications, WinRM module import helpers, PSGet
        integration, etc.
